<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://GeekGhc.github.io/post-images/1616430515453.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<!-- more -->
<h2 id="安装">安装</h2>
<h3 id="1clone到本地">1.clone到本地</h3>
<pre><code class="language-shell">$ git clone https://github.com/GeekGhc/adminLTE-for-laravel.git
</code></pre>
<h3 id="2根目录下创建env文件">2.根目录下创建.env文件</h3>
<pre><code class="language-shell"> $ php artisan key:generate
</code></pre>
<p>后台开发过程时可借助<code>MustBeAnAdmin</code> middleware 完成逻辑判断</p>
<p>在管理用户权限的<code>Packages</code></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://github.com/spatie/laravel-permission">Laravel Permission</a> 目前我的项目就是用的这个<code>Package</code></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/romanbican/roles">Laravel Roles</a></li>
<li><a href="https://github.com/ultraware/roles">ultraware/roles</a></li>
</ul>
